  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A cute baby slime has drifted through space and landed on a strange planet.<br>Begin a brave journey to reunite with the mommy slime!<br>Control the slime to explore complex terrains, overcome dangerous obstacles, and create a heartwarming moment of reunion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● <strong>Help the slime with your mouse.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3473540/extras/db0f694850e7554f4af00e929d416198.avif?t=1740641881\" width=640 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can drag the slime with your mouse to move it around.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● <strong>Customize your slime.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3473540/extras/52ecc5dd2978619a77522319d55e554a.avif?t=1740641881\" width=640 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Freely customize the slime's face, body, and accessories to create your very own unique slime.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Supports mouse and keyboard only</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A cute baby slime has drifted through space and landed on a strange planet.<br>Begin a brave journey to reunite with the mommy slime!<br>Control the slime to explore complex terrains, overcome dangerous obstacles, and create a heartwarming moment of reunion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● <strong>Help the slime with your mouse.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3473540/extras/db0f694850e7554f4af00e929d416198.avif?t=1740641881\" width=640 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can drag the slime with your mouse to move it around.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● <strong>Customize your slime.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3473540/extras/52ecc5dd2978619a77522319d55e554a.avif?t=1740641881\" width=640 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Freely customize the slime's face, body, and accessories to create your very own unique slime.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Supports mouse and keyboard only</p>",
